response.overview: On August 20th is the second part of GCW: Homecoming 2023 live on FITE+ straight from Showboat Atlantic city. The event features the GCW World Title Match where Blake Christian defends his title against Masha Slamovich.  Also in the lineup:  Dragon Kid vs Komander Maki Itoh vs B3CCA  GCW Tag Team Title Match The East West Express (Jordan Oliver & Nick Wayne) (c) vs ??? & Takashi Sasaki  Tag Team Match Dante Leon & Ninja Mack vs Alec Price & Cole Radrick  GCW Ultraviolent Title Match Rina Yamashita (c) vs Violento Jack
response.title: GCW Homecoming Weekend 2023, Part 2
